<item>
            <title>[LU-10850] empty indexes don&apos;t iterate correctly on ldiskfs</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10850</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When iterating through an empty ldiskfs regular index I see a single &quot;ghost&quot; record which is zerod out. Specifically, when given an empty regular ldiskfs index, load() returns 1 which is wrong. ZFS indexes do not show this issue.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
